{"tid":179841,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我的天是灰色　我的心是藍色","createTime":"2017-03-30T13:33:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-30T17:57:31.000Z","uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0f9ab16235c1da29d6d7b4ff51be366337b6f964","tid":179841,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T13:33:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/battle.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 學友學友永遠支持你<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我的天是灰色　我的心是藍色<br />\n觸摸著你的心　竟是透明的<br />\n<br />\n你的悠然自得　我卻束手無策<br />\n我的心痛竟是　你的快樂<br />\n<br />\n其實我不想對你戀戀不捨　但什麼讓我輾轉反側<br />\n不覺我說著說著天就亮了　我的唇角嘗到一種苦澀<br />\n<br />\n我是真的為你哭了　你是真的隨他走了<br />\n就在這一刻全世界傷心角色　又多了我一個<br />\n<br />\n我是真的為你愛了　你是真的跟他走了<br />\n能給的我全都給了　我都捨得<br />\n除了讓你知道　我心如刀割<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/OWy1rHBVGgk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FOWy1rHBVGgk&d=xSG8yb8yy9PjQoJ4RYEJZP9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=6cd93121\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/OWy1rHBVGgk</a>"},{"pid":"eaa2587ed1730bbf551d05960de1b3f607dd3c2e","tid":179841,"uid":4210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T13:37:04.000Z","msg":"我愛黎明 我愛黎明"},{"pid":"01e3ee6bb7d77ac4c6a56579d2b56ab15bae8d49","tid":179841,"uid":85537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T17:57:31.000Z","msg":"真心英雄"}]}